hopobject.body: How many would you like? k m pharmacy labelle fl Young would have been an ideal fit for the Bombers, who have been in need of a righthanded-hitting first baseman as well as another option at third base. Lyle Overbay will continue to play first base on a daily basis, while Jayson Nix and Brent Lillibridge appear to be the primary options at third base with Alex Rodriguez expected to be suspended by Major League Baseball later this week. Eduardo Nunez could also be given a look at third base.
